      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain delivers power to the rear wheels via a speed-sensitive variable M differential lock. The chassis benefits from a well-sorted suspension geometry, providing the communicative feedback characteristic of this platform. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and inspection of the rear subframe mounting points. A mechanically robust example, this M3 offers a visceral driving experience with the precision expected of an M-division icon.",
